      <akn:section eId="sec_28:8_508">
        <akn:num>28:8-508</akn:num>
        <akn:heading>Duty of securities intermediary to change entitlement holderâ€™s position to other form of security holding.</akn:heading>
<akn:subsection eId="subsec_28:8-508_1">
      <akn:num>(1)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>The securities intermediary acts as agreed upon by the entitlement holder and the securities intermediary; or</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_28:8-508_2">
      <akn:num>(2)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>In the absence of agreement, the securities intermediary exercises due care in accordance with reasonable commercial standards to follow the direction of the entitlement holder.</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection>
